{"tid":2326592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔新浪潭路再奪一命　外籍單車男自炒送院亡","createTime":"2020-12-15T12:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:21:45.000Z","uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56070ed31c76d9ee18c103d866e2d09b7cffd0be","tid":2326592,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"繼昨晚大埔新浪潭路有私家車撞燈柱導致男司機身亡的意外後，今晚（15日）再發生奪命車禍。傍晚6時13分，一名外籍男子騎單車沿新浪潭路而行，騎至近新娘潭路燒烤區涌背段時，懷疑失控自炒，外籍男倒地受傷，有人報警求助。救護員到場，外籍男昏迷不醒，送往那打素醫院後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方正調查意外原因。大埔新浪潭路兩日奪兩命，上址路段迂迴曲折，路窄而且多彎位，以往曾發生多次致命交通意外。昨晚約9時39分，一輛白色本田思域Type R沿新娘潭路往大尾督方向行駛，途至近燒烤區1號場對開右彎時失控，猛撼燈柱及創入草叢內，車身幾乎斷開兩截。姓梁（20歲）男司機被困車內，由消防救出時，頭部嚴重受傷昏迷，送院搶救後不治"},{"pid":"f949e68c21d3bdc589f0322421ff6eb4ac504504","tid":2326592,"uid":29969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"From支01"},{"pid":"37fd2f4b4b3ded623d0a131577b69f89c2f333f1","tid":2326592,"uid":83388,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72ac5f6c2cd9c9195562267c27f3f0a34950562","tid":2326592,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37fd2f4b4b3ded623d0a131577b69f89c2f333f1","tid":2326592,"uid":83388,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"你將會死全家"},{"pid":"98e91b880fdba69ae24dd0bcf5143c947c3c37fc","tid":2326592,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":